        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(C = \\begin{pmatrix} a_1\\cr \\vdots\\cr\na_n \\end{pmatrix} \\in \\mathcal{M}_{n,1}(\\R)\\)</span> et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(M = C{}^tC\\)</span>.</p>\n"
